        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 2. Daphnia sinevi s.str., adult male from a puddle near reservoir of Luchegorskaya power station, Primorski Territory, Russia, AAK M-651.A, adult male. B–D, its head, lateral view. E, anterior and ventral margin of valves. F, setae at ventral margin. G–I, armature of postero-ventral and posterior margin. J–K, caudal spine. L–M, postabdomen. N–P, armature of postabdominal claw. Scale bars denote 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4398091/files/figure.png" .

